data.description: WOW! CHARMING 5 BR 2.5 BATH home in sought-after Eagle Village! AWARD WINNING AUBREY ISD! Warm & welcoming covered front porch and heavily shaded front yard. Fantastic open floor plan with GORGEOUS NEW Herringbone wood like tile floors & NEW CARPET! Downstairs bedroom can also be an office. Completely renovated kitchen with custom cabinets, granite countertops, backsplash, & pantry. Great size spare bedrooms with large closets. Spacious master bedroom with dual sinks, garden tub, & separate shower, & large walk in closet! Great backyard with open patio. MUST SEE!!!
